Package: validationplot
Type: Package
Title: Hosmer-Lemeshow Test Plot (http://github.com/avantcredit/make_validation_plot)
Description: R plotting tools for visualizing a Hosmer-Lemeshow
    goodness-of-fit test on a binary classifier.
